			<ns0:name>pdox%goo...@gtempaccount.com</ns0:name><ns0:uri>/u/104735739662288482898/</ns0:uri></ns0:author><ns0:content type="html">In the PNaCl newlib build, libgcc_eh.a is currently built in single-threaded mode, so that there is no thread safety. This could cause problems in multi-threaded applications that throw exceptions from multiple threads.

libgcc_eh should be built in a thread-safe way. To avoid adding additional dependencies on libc, this can be done using intrinsics / spin locks.</ns0:content><ns0:updated>2012-02-15T19:04:57.000Z</ns0:updated><ns0:published>2011-12-15T01:45:10.000Z</ns0:published><ns2:status>New</ns2:status><ns2:owner>
